{"tid":870334,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘意睇書既巴絲打入一入黎","createTime":"2018-10-21T04:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T13:12:54.000Z","uid":6370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1628e3326d2d224b6387c3db1c52c15b8808adf6","tid":870334,"uid":6370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"屋企太多書越買越多，越積越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捐書又多多限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔收錢放曬出黎睇下有無有緣人接收佢地，<br />\n全部都好新架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先到先得 <br />\n至於點交收或者郵寄大家就一就啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1    1367 <br />\n2    哈利波特穿越魔法史 <br />\n3    人類大歷史<br />\n4    中國歷史穿越指南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5    你所不安的事 有九成都不會發生<br />\n6    no sleep 無眠書<br />\n7    被消失的 MH350<br />\n8    西營盤 <br />\n9    故事的解剖<br />\n10   在咖啡冷掉之前<br />\n11   從古人生活學文化常識<br />\n12   活在古代不容易<br />\n13   暗黑森林<br />\n14   廁所裡的哲學課<br />\n15   我不是 我自己<br />\n16   犯罪人格 剖繪檔案<br />\n17   飢餓遊戲 3 集<br />\n18   移動迷宮 3 集<br />\n19   你所煩惱的事有九成不會發生<br />\n20   天才在左 瘋子在右<br />\n21   自願被吃的豬<br />\n22   33 天之後<br />\n23   瘋人院臥底十日紀<br />\n24   印度風物記"},{"pid":"44adb7664284390f4745cfd334607984ba1ce384","tid":870334,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"樓主好重口味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"